{"title":"Macworld Podcast 735: The past and future of the HomePod and iMac","link":"https://www.macworld.com/article/340362/macworld-podcast-735-the-past-and-future-of-the-homepod-and-imac.html","date":1616677200000,"content":"<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0 Transitional//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/loose.dtd\">\n<html><body><div id=\"link_wrapped_content\">\n<section class=\"wp-block-bigbite-multi-title\"><div class=\"container\"></div></section><p>Deep inside the&nbsp;HomePod&nbsp;mini is a secret.&nbsp;Will&nbsp;Apple ever reveal it to the public? What&rsquo;s not so secret&nbsp;are the reason why Apple decided to&nbsp;end to&nbsp;the original&nbsp;HomePod&nbsp;and the iMac Pro.&nbsp;We memorialize these products and look to the&nbsp;future in this episode of the Macworld Podcast.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"read-more\">Read more&nbsp;</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Learn more about the topics we discussed on the show.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/340158/the-homepod-mini-has-a-secret-temperature-sensor.html\" target=\"_blank\">The HomePod mini has a secret temperature sensor that doesn&rsquo;t do anything</a></li><li><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/339493/how-the-homepod-mini-can-succeed-where-apples-first-smart-speaker-failed.html\" target=\"_blank\">How the HomePod mini can succeed where Apple&rsquo;s first smart speaker failed</a></li><li><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/334315/apple-discontinues-imac-pro-as-signs-point-to-imminent-m1-launch.html\" target=\"_blank\">Apple discontinues iMac Pro as M1 redesign of Apple&rsquo;s iconic all-in-one looms</a></li><li><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/338555/the-imac-pro-was-the-ultimate-intel-mac-of-its-era.html\" target=\"_blank\">Requiem for the iMac Pro, the ultimate Mac of the Intel era</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/340370/an-act-of-desperation-20-years-ago-formed-the-building-block-for-the-modern-mac.html\">An act of desperation 20 years ago was the building block for the modern Mac</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/340395/from-aqua-to-catalina-the-evolution-of-the-mac-os-x-operating-system.html\">From Aqua to Catalina: The evolution of macOS X</a></li></ul><h2 id=\"how-to-subscribe-to-the-macworld-podcast\">How to subscribe to the Macworld Podcast</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>You can subscribe to the Macworld Podcast&mdash;or leave us a review!&mdash;<a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=111346X1569486&amp;url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/id563933198&amp;xcust=1-1-340362-0-0-0&amp;sref=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" rel=\"nofollow\">right in the Podcasts app</a>. Or you can point your favorite podcast-savvy RSS reader at: <code>http://feeds.soundcloud.com/users/58576458-macworld/tracks</code></p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Macworld Podcast is also <a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=111346X1569486&amp;url=https://open.spotify.com/show/3uyZkE4tjbwNNrJCLsBUAM?si=OdOljEAYQvC_ewEsMfKzXA&amp;xcust=1-1-340362-0-0-0&amp;sref=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" rel=\"nofollow\">available on Spotify</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To find previous episodes, visit <a href=\"http://www.macworld.com/column/mwpodcast\">Macworld&rsquo;s podcast page</a> or our home on <a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=111346X1569486&amp;url=http://www.soundcloud.com/macworld&amp;xcust=1-1-340362-0-0-0&amp;sref=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" rel=\"nofollow\">Soundcloud</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is episode 735 with&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.macworld.com/author/Jason-Cross/\" target=\"_blank\">Jason Cross</a>,&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.macworld.com/author/Michael-Simon/\" target=\"_blank\">Michael Simon</a>, and&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.macworld.com/author/Roman-Loyola/\" target=\"_blank\">Roman Loyola</a